{"tid":650015,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"債務沉重 結他名牌Gibson申請破產","createTime":"2018-05-02T03:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T14:31:47.000Z","uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"72a508a73c3edfa41a64f07752a4c2c01681e0af","tid":650015,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T03:23:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180502/58142290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180502%2F58142290&d=nRHBUVZHhqwhhyqBOnRgtLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=8a21f58b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180502%2F58142290&h=1317a83d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180502/58142290</a><br />\n<br />\n 結他名牌Gibson Brands在連串收購後債台高築，周二申請破產保護。<br />\n<br />\nGibson在特拉華州的美國破產法庭，提出申請在《美國破產法》第11章下進行自願破產保護。該公司表示，破產保護期間他們會繼續營運，專注重組核心業務，計劃逐步終止主要在美國境外經營的Gibson&rsquo;s Innovations業務。<br />\n<br />\n自從多年前開始收購家居娛樂及音響設備製造商，Gibson一直受到沉重債務困擾。它收購的公司包括部份Royal Phillips的家居娛樂系統、TEAC及Onkyo stereos。<br />\n<br />\nGibson於1894年創立，旗下傳奇品牌包括Les Paul和SG，「貓王」皮禮士利（Elvis Presley）最喜歡的原聲吉他就是Gibson J-200。Gibson總部位於納什維爾（Nashville），每年在逾80個國家賣出超過17萬支結他。"},{"pid":"5c90d944066274811973d61c936da10871b9aebc","tid":650015,"uid":173786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T03:25:53.000Z","msg":"gibson 都要破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde0e8fb0add9a75292dffc24a98fea62708adc2","tid":650015,"uid":17330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c90d944066274811973d61c936da10871b9aebc","tid":650015,"uid":173786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T03:25:53.000Z","msg":"gibson 都要破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T03:26:56.000